{"tid":628621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山東地鐵免費試搭   大媽變「喪屍」逼爆地鐵站 網民：中國特色","createTime":"2018-04-14T04:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T07:08:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f9cf48a22da0086c8c419ecf71045bcd7f38077e","tid":628621,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180414/large/1523672714_99f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180414%2Flarge%2F1523672714_99f8.jpg&h=b9481c0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即使醜態盡露，中國人也不會放過任何能獲得小便宜的機會。山東青島地鐵11號線即將正式營運。當局安排4月13日至15日，展開為期3天的市民試乘體驗，民眾可以免費試乘。<br />\n<br />\n無數大媽大叔把握機會，即時蜂擁到地鐵站。由於人太多，即使工作人員如何努力，也難敵大媽大叔的熱情，眾人有如力大無窮的「喪屍」，連圍欄也被推開。據悉，為了為應付試乘的人數，試乘時間延長一天至4月16日。<br />\n對於民眾為了免費乘搭，瞬即逼爆地鐵站，網民紛紛留言：<br />\n小兔兔不是小破兔：有病<br />\n貳妜笙：沒坐過地鐵？<br />\nRs、6：看著都惡心<br />\n大緣仔的主人：中國特色<br />\n僵絲丸子：貪小便宜<br />\n暴走族jr：行屍走肉既視感！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180414/58071533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F58071533&d=WxIVqh6e2MKgQ83lfIU2XMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=630908db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F58071533&h=37a1f60b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180414/58071533</a>"},{"pid":"fa192878c887b6e668c5ffbff9cf1fc2537e45d4","tid":628621,"uid":1367,"like":11,"dislike":12,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:50:28.000Z","msg":"香港其實都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724714bb99f2d4d3752f8757a6ea622eb66fa039","tid":628621,"uid":40628,"like":4,"dislike"